title: DUO QUEUE JUNGLER OR TOP LANER
body:
I'm a mid lane main and I'm looking for a person to duo queue with preferably top or jg.
Looking to go to gold this season. 
State your : Age
                    Name ( First name )
                    How long you've been playing
                    What times you can play.

replies.body:
G'day,
I'm a top main from Australia.
My name's james and i'm 16 yrs old.
I've played since s3 but stopped at the end of s5 and just recently started again.
My goal is also to reach gold this season :D

Sup,
Supoprt main but will wreck shit up with voli at top or jg
Hit me up at Lord ThranduiI for more info.
